sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Claude
    participant S as MCP Server
    participant I as Yahoo IMAP

    C->>S: apply_action(action, uid[], source_folder)

    S->>S: Resolve source_folder<br/>(default: "INBOX")
    S->>S: Look up action in action table

    alt Action not found
        S-->>C: Error: InvalidActionError
    end

    S->>I: Acquire mailbox lock on source_folder

    loop For each UID in batch
        S->>I: FETCH uid from source_folder (uid: true)

        alt UID not found
            S->>S: Record error for this UID
        else UID found
            alt Action has folder (move target)
                S->>I: messageFlagsAdd(\\Seen) if mark_read
                S->>I: messageFlagsAdd(\\Flagged) if flag
                S->>I: messageMove(uid, action.folder)
            else No folder (stays in place)
                S->>I: messageFlagsAdd(\\Seen) if mark_read
                S->>I: messageFlagsAdd(\\Flagged) if flag
            end
            S->>S: Log to audit.jsonl
        end
    end

    S->>I: Release mailbox lock
    S-->>C: { applied: N, errors: M, results[] }

    Note over C,S: Max 20 UIDs per call to avoid timeout
